'''易卜拉欣·马赫莱卜'''（{{lang-ar|إبراهيم محلب}}；Ibrahim Mahlab；{{bd|1949年|4月12日|catIdx=M}})，又译“易卜拉欣·马格赖布”，前任[[埃及總理|埃及總理]]。

== 總理 ==
2014年2月25日埃及临时总理[[哈齐姆·贝卜拉维|哈齐姆·贝卜拉维]]辞职，临时总统[[阿德利·曼苏尔|阿德利·曼苏尔]]授权时任住房、公共工程与城市化部长的马赫莱卜组建新内阁<ref>{{Citation|url=http://www.lfxinwen.cn/a/guoji/2014/02/2774.html|title=埃及临时总统授权马格赖布任临时总理组阁|date=2014年2月25日|accessdate=25 February 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714225708/http://www.lfxinwen.cn/a/guoji/2014/02/2774.html|archive-date=2014年7月14日|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。3月1日，马赫莱卜任[[埃及总理|总理]]的埃及临时政府新内阁32名成员在首都开罗向临时总统曼苏尔宣誓就职。<ref>{{Citation|url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2014/03-02/5898907.shtml|title=埃及临时政府新内阁宣誓就职赛西留任原职|work=中国新闻网|date=2014年3月1日|accessdate=2014年3月2日|archive-date=2019年5月22日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190522100650/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2014/03-02/5898907.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

马赫莱卜已婚，会讲英语和法语。<ref name="aljaz">{{Citation|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2014/02/egypt-housing-minister-form-new-government-2014225123636437550.html|title=Egypt housing minister to form new government|work=Al Jazeera English|date=25 February 2014|accessdate=25 February 2014|archive-date=2014-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302041139/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2014/02/egypt-housing-minister-form-new-government-2014225123636437550.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 政策 ===
[[2013年埃及政变|2013年埃及政变]]以来，马赫莱卜在[[哈齐姆·贝卜拉维|哈齐姆·贝卜拉维]]的临时政府中担任住房部长，<ref>{{Citation|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/feb/25/egypt-new-prime-minister-ibrahim-mahlab|title=Egypt names Ibrahim Mahlab as new prime minister|work=The Guardian|date=25 February 2014|accessdate=25 February 2014|archive-date=2019-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191115141212/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/feb/25/egypt-new-prime-minister-ibrahim-mahlab|dead-url=no}}</ref>贝卜拉维辞职后，马赫莱卜被任命为新一届临时政府总理。<ref>{{Citation|url=http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/1/64/95208/Egypt/Politics-/Ibrahim-Mehleb-to-form-new-Egypt-government.aspx|title=Ibrahim Mehleb to form new Egypt government|work=Ahram Online|date=25 February 2014|accessdate=25 February 2014|archive-date=2019-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190521185225/http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/1/64/95208/Egypt/Politics-/Ibrahim-Mehleb-to-form-new-Egypt-government.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>他说他的政府将“继续致力于维护社会稳定和打击恐怖主义”。他也宣称会重建经济。<ref>{{Citation|url=http://en.aswatmasriya.com/news/view.aspx?id=d9640263-334f-4049-9f50-3f2583eb5254|title=Egypt's new PM says to fight militancy, rebuild economy|work=Aswat Masriya|date=25 February 2014|accessdate=25 February 2014|archive-date=2014-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141205062747/http://en.aswatmasriya.com/news/view.aspx?id=d9640263-334f-4049-9f50-3f2583eb5254|dead-url=no}}</ref>

